<div class="min-h-screen bg-base-200 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Nailed It!</h1>

    <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">What is Nailed It!?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Nailed It! is an AI-powered technical interview preparation platform designed to help students and early-career developers build confidence and master the skills needed to succeed in tech interviews.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our platform simulates realistic interview scenarios using advanced AI technology, providing instant feedback and personalized guidance to help you improve with every practice session.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">How It Works</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl mr-3">1.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Choose Your Interview</h3>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Select from a variety of technical interview scenarios tailored to different roles and difficulty levels.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl mr-3">2.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Practice with AI</h3>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Engage in realistic conversations with our AI interviewer that adapts to your responses and provides challenging follow-up questions.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl mr-3">3.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Get Feedback & Improve</h3>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Receive instant, constructive feedback on your performance and learn from each session to continuously improve your interview skills.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We believe that everyone deserves a fair chance to showcase their technical skills and land their dream job in tech. Traditional interview preparation can be expensive, time-consuming, and often inaccessible. Nailed It! democratizes interview preparation by providing affordable, on-demand practice that fits your schedule and learning pace.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Technology</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Nailed It! leverages cutting-edge artificial intelligence and natural language processing to create an authentic interview experience. Our AI interviewer is trained on real interview patterns and technical concepts, ensuring you get realistic practice that prepares you for the real world.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info mb-8">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">Disclaimer</h3>
        <div class="text-sm mt-2">
          <p class="mb-2">Nailed It! is an educational tool designed to help you practice and improve your technical interview skills. While we strive to provide realistic and valuable practice experiences, please note:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>AI-generated feedback is meant to be helpful guidance, not definitive evaluation</li>
            <li>Real interviews may vary significantly from our simulations</li>
            <li>This platform is a supplement to, not a replacement for, comprehensive interview preparation</li>
            <li>Results and performance on this platform do not guarantee success in actual job interviews</li>
            <li>We recommend using this tool as part of a broader preparation strategy that includes studying, coding practice, and mock interviews with peers or mentors</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <%= link_to "Start Practicing", interviews_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
